missionEventData.data1: We have traced the arms used in the recent attack on Outpost D-34 to a Mugaari cargo loading area in the Tungra Sector.  We suspect that the Mugaari are providing arms and other aid to the Rebels. Our attack on this cargo area is timed to catch the Mugaari and Rebels in their next illicit weapons exchange. Your mission objective is to destroy all cargo-carrying vessels at this site. Destroy everything, take no prisoners.
The enemy is already beginning to move. Switch to torpedos and fire at will!
Well done! All Mugaari freighters have been destroyed.
Excellent! All Rebel transports have been destroyed.
All enemy shuttles have been destroyed.
There are still rebel ships active. Take them out.
Well done. Return to the Fogger at once. We're moving out immediately!
Beta 3 you've picked up a tail. Recommend you try to shake him before you continue to attack.

missionEventData.data2: At the battle of Yavin Rebel terrorists, aided by spies and traitors within the Empire, struck a cowardly blow at the new symbol of Imperial power... The Death Star! Darth Vader brought swift justice to the Rebels by destroying their main base on Hoth. The pitiful remnants of the Alliance have now scattered to the Outer Rim. In the days ahead, the Emperor will call upon the Imperial Navy to eradicate the last vestiges of rebellion and restore law and order to the galaxy!
